								* 본인의 이름을 입력해야 결제시 입금 확인이 가능합니다
							</div>
							<div class="btnBox">

							</div>
							<div class="buttonBox">
								<input type="submit" name="" id="" value="가입하기">
							</div>
						</div>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
			<!-- Footer -->
			<div id="footer">
				<div style="text-align: center;">Copyright © 1998-2021 KH Information Educational Institute All Right Reserved</div>
